| **Detached branches** | Often separate session / phrase | Invoked via `development-process.md` branch names | Automatic Squad Leader spawn from §§1–5 |

**Host rules:** each `AGENT_RUN_REQUEST_V1` opens a child lane; parent waits for `AGENT_RESULT_RESPONSE_V1` when the skill says so. Squad Leader **§7** tracks planning `activeLanes`, `openLedgerEntries`, `spawnedPlans`, `remainingTasks`; **§8** tracks ship rows per PR plan — it does not re-run detached child skills from the leader lane.

