## Protocol

Session command phrases are declared in `mission.yaml`. **§§1–7** define Squad Leader routing for **planning** on **`plan and deliver`**. **§8** defines Squad Leader **ship cadence oversight** and **dispatch resolution gates** while implementation/ship skills still execute as **detached** branches (see **Squad operations** — the Squad Leader does **not** spawn **`coding-session`**, **`pre-pr-review`**, **`create-pr`**, etc. from §§1–7).

```mermaid
